<item>
            <title>[LU-16884] Poor Lustre performace with NFS reexport</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16884</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We see poor performance for reading / accessing data via NFS reexport from lustre &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;eg :-&lt;br/&gt;
On lustre client machine&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;08Jun2023 6:17pm vvv@oscar1:/u/vvv&amp;gt; /usr/bin/time -f%e find /user_data/ARCHIVE/HALFWAY/far_057_0790/ | wc -l
16.03
251889
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;On some other machine via NFS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;08Jun2023 6:17pm vvv@una:/u/vvv&amp;gt; /usr/bin/time -f%e find /hosts/oscar1/user_data/ARCHIVE/HALFWAY/far_057_0790/ | wc -l
3143.13
251889
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please let us know what all more information and logs you need to check this issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards,&lt;br/&gt;
Viral Vadalia&lt;/p&gt;</description>
